<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Booking confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; line-height: 1.5; padding: 24px; }
      h1   { color: #0a6dbf; margin-bottom: 0; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #e1e4e8; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; max-width: 520px; }
      dl { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr; gap: 6px 12px; margin: 0; }
      dt { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
      dd { margin: 0; }
      .footer { color: #777; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>You have booked your ticket ✈️</h1>
    <p>Hi <%= @passenger.name %>,</p>
    <p>Thanks for booking with Flight Booker. Your seat is confirmed — see the details below.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <dl>
        <dt>From</dt>      <dd><%= @flight.from_airport %></dd>
        <dt>To</dt>        <dd><%= @flight.to_airport %></dd>
        <dt>Departure</dt> <dd><%= @flight.departure.strftime("%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M") %></dd>
        <dt>Arrival</dt>   <dd><%= @flight.arrival.strftime("%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M") %></dd>
        <dt>Duration</dt>  <dd><%= @flight.duration %> minutes</dd>
        <dt>Booking ref</dt><dd>#<%= @flight.id %></dd>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <p>Please arrive at the airport at least 90 minutes before departure.</p>

    <p class="footer">
      Sent by Flight Booker • This is an automated message, please do not reply.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>